**1. SYSTEM OVERVIEW**

**1.1 Mission & Core Principle**

CorpFit is a B2B2C corporate wellness platform (\'Circle of Resilient
People\'). The QUANTUM AI Content Factory is a fully autonomous
multi-agent system that discovers trending wellness topics, generates
brand-compliant content, produces AI videos, and publishes to social
media --- all managed from a phone via Telegram.

**NORTH STAR:** \"Making health, losing weight, losing fat is FUN.\" ---
Every feature, every piece of content, every decision must pass this
test.

