**4. DATABASE SCHEMA (PostgreSQL)**

Database: corpfit_db \| 8 tables total

**4.1 trend_board**

Stores discovered wellness trends from ELECTRON-1.

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Column**    **Type**    **Nullable**   **Description**
  ------------- ----------- -------------- -----------------------------------------
  id            SERIAL PK   No             Auto-increment primary key

  trend_name    TEXT        No             Trend title

  score         INTEGER     No             Relevance score (0--100)

  module        TEXT        No             Steps / Workouts / Meals / Check-in /
                                           Events

  source        TEXT        Yes            Source where trend was discovered

  created_at    TIMESTAMP   No             Discovery timestamp (DEFAULT NOW())
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

**4.2 content_briefs**

Production briefs created by QUANTUM planner.

  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Column**       **Type**    **Nullable**   **Description**
  ---------------- ----------- -------------- -----------------------------------------
  id               SERIAL PK   No             Auto-increment primary key

  topic            TEXT        No             Content topic

  module           TEXT        No             Target module
                                              (Steps/Workouts/Meals/Check-in/Events)

  platform         TEXT        No             TikTok / Instagram / LinkedIn / YouTube

  funnel           TEXT        No             B2C or B2B

  duration         INTEGER     Yes            Target video duration in seconds

  status           TEXT        No             pending / approved / rejected / published
                                              / killed

  brief_data       JSONB       Yes            Full brief JSON (trend score, angle,
                                              hooks)

  content_log_id   INTEGER FK  Yes            FK to content_logs.id (set after E2 runs)

  created_at       TIMESTAMP   No             Creation timestamp
  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

**4.3 content_logs**

Generated content from ELECTRON-2. Includes full cost tracking.

  ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Column**      **Type**    **Nullable**   **Description**
  --------------- ----------- -------------- -----------------------------------------
  id              SERIAL PK   No             Auto-increment primary key

  brief_id        INTEGER FK  No             FK to content_briefs.id

  script          TEXT        Yes            Full timed video script

  hook            TEXT        Yes            Primary hook (best of 3)

  hooks_json      JSONB       Yes            All 3 hooks as JSON array

  cta             TEXT        Yes            Call to action text

  caption_short   TEXT        Yes            Short social caption

  caption_long    TEXT        Yes            Long caption with hashtags

  onscreen_text   TEXT        Yes            On-screen overlay text

  storyboard      TEXT        Yes            Scene-by-scene visual description

  disclaimer      TEXT        Yes            Health/safety disclaimer

  qa_scores       JSONB       Yes            Gate 1/2/3 results (pass, violations,
                                             confidence)

  qa_passed       BOOLEAN     Yes            Overall QA pass/fail

  model_used      TEXT        Yes            claude-sonnet-4-20250514

  input_tokens    INTEGER     Yes            Actual input tokens from API response

  output_tokens   INTEGER     Yes            Actual output tokens from API response

  e2_cost         NUMERIC     Yes            Content generation cost (USD)

  qa_cost         NUMERIC     Yes            QA gates cost (USD) --- 3 Haiku calls

  total_cost      NUMERIC     Yes            e2_cost + qa_cost

  created_at      TIMESTAMP   No             Generation timestamp
  ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

**4.4 publish_logs**

Video production records from ELECTRON-3.

  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Column**       **Type**    **Nullable**   **Description**
  ---------------- ----------- -------------- -----------------------------------------
  id               SERIAL PK   No             Auto-increment primary key

  brief_id         INTEGER FK  No             FK to content_briefs.id

  content_log_id   INTEGER FK  No             FK to content_logs.id

  video_tool       TEXT        No             kling / veo / heygen / synthesia / pika

  video_url        TEXT        Yes            URL of produced video file

  status           TEXT        No             processing / ready_to_post / failed

  resolution       TEXT        Yes            e.g. 1080x1920

  duration_sec     INTEGER     Yes            Actual video duration

  created_at       TIMESTAMP   No             Production timestamp
  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

**4.5 schedule_logs**

ORBIT scheduling records --- one row per platform per video.

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Column**          **Type**      **Nullable**   **Description**
  ------------------- ------------- -------------- ---------------------------------------
  id                  SERIAL PK     No             Auto-increment primary key

  publish_log_id      INTEGER FK    No             FK to publish_logs.id

  content_log_id      INTEGER FK    No             FK to content_logs.id

  brief_id            INTEGER FK    No             FK to content_briefs.id

  platform            VARCHAR(20)   No             tiktok / instagram / linkedin

  status              VARCHAR(30)   No             queued / uploading / processing / live
                                                   / failed / held

  platform_post_id    TEXT          Yes            Native post ID from platform API

  platform_post_url   TEXT          Yes            Public URL of the live post

  caption             TEXT          Yes            Caption sent with the post

  hashtags            TEXT          Yes            Hashtags (JSON array)

  scheduled_at        TIMESTAMPTZ   Yes            When post is scheduled for

  posted_at           TIMESTAMPTZ   Yes            When post actually went live

  error_message       TEXT          Yes            Error details if status = failed

  retry_count         INTEGER       No             Number of retry attempts (max 3)

  mode_used           VARCHAR(10)   No             manual / semi / auto

  operator_id         TEXT          Yes            Telegram user ID of approving operator

  created_at          TIMESTAMPTZ   No             Row creation timestamp

  updated_at          TIMESTAMPTZ   No             Last update timestamp
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

