  Analytics        Node         timeline (by day), cost totals (from
                                content_logs cost columns), counts by
                                module, counts by platform, QA compliance
                                trend over time

  Format Analytics Code Node    Structures query results into
                                Chart.js-compatible JSON arrays

  Respond to       Respond to   Returns chart data arrays to Cloudflare
