**6.11 Error Logger (v1)**

3-node centralized error sink. Every workflow\'s error handler POSTs
here.

  ------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Node Name      **Type**     **Detail**
  (exact)**                     
  ---------------- ------------ ------------------------------------------
  Webhook          Webhook      POST --- receives error payloads from all
                                workflows. URL: /webhook/error-logger

  Store Error      PostgreSQL   executeQuery --- INSERT into error_logs
                   Node         (workflow, error_type, error_message,
                                retry_count, resolved=false)

  Respond to       Respond to   Acknowledges receipt so calling workflow
  Webhook          Webhook Node can continue
  ------------------------------------------------------------------------

