**8.4 How to Update the Knowledge Base**

-   Edit the setup script: C:\\FunFit\\funfit_qdrant_setup.py

-   Add/modify entries in BRAND_RULES or BANNED_PHRASES lists

-   Run: python C:\\FunFit\\funfit_qdrant_setup.py

-   Script deletes old collections and recreates them from scratch

-   Changes take effect immediately --- next E2 run uses updated rules

**WARNING:** Running the setup script deletes and recreates both
collections. Always back up the script before making changes.

**8.5 Adding a Brand Rule**

{ \"id\": 80, \"category\": \"modules\", \"title\": \"Sleep Module\",

\"content\": \"The Sleep module covers sleep hygiene, rest
optimization\...\" }

**8.6 Adding a Banned Phrase**

{ \"id\": 200, \"category\": \"banned_weight\", \"phrase\": \"diet\",

\"reason\": \"Diet culture language --- promotes restriction mentality\"
}

