  publish              Stage 2       brief.status →         Wait 2-5 min for video
                       (Content      \'published\'. E3      preview
                       review)       triggered via webhook. 

  kill                 Stage 2       brief.status →         Done --- content
                       (Content      \'killed\'. No video   archived
                       review)       produced.              

  platform_tiktok      Stage 3       schedule_logs row      ORBIT Publisher picks
                       (ORBIT        created for TikTok     up within 5 min
                       scheduling)   (status: queued)       

  platform_instagram   Stage 3       schedule_logs row      ORBIT Publisher picks
                       (ORBIT        created for Instagram  up within 5 min
                       scheduling)   (status: queued)       

  platform_linkedin    Stage 3       schedule_logs row      ORBIT Publisher picks
                       (ORBIT        created for LinkedIn   up within 5 min
                       scheduling)   (status: queued)       

  platform_all         Stage 3       3 schedule_logs rows   All 3 platforms queued
                       (ORBIT        created (one per       
                       scheduling)   platform)              

  platform_hold        Stage 3       No schedule_logs       Manually re-trigger
                       (ORBIT        created. Video stays   via /orbit later
                       scheduling)   in publish_logs.       
  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------

**10.3 Commands**

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Command**          **Handler**        **Response**
  -------------------- ------------------ ------------------------------------
  /status              System Health      Complete system health: trends
                       Check workflow     count, briefs, content, videos,
                                          errors, last activity per agent

  /stale               Stale Brief Check  List of briefs pending or approved
                       workflow           \>24h without action

  /backup              Backup Manager     Triggers manual DB snapshot +
                       workflow           service health report

  /help                Approval Handler   Full command list with descriptions
                       (inline)           

  /orbit_status        Approval Handler   ORBIT queue summary:
                       (inline)           Queued/Publishing/Published/Failed
                                          counts per platform

  /orbit_queue         Approval Handler   Detailed list of all active
                       (inline)           schedule_logs items

  /orbit_mode          Approval Handler   Switches orbit_mode in
  manual\|semi\|auto   (inline)           system_config. Confirms change via
                                          Telegram.

  /orbit               Triggers ORBIT     Immediately processes all queued
                       Publisher webhook  schedule_logs items
