**11.3 Cost Tracking Implementation**

Real-time cost tracking was implemented after discovering a \$4.76
discrepancy between estimated dashboard costs and actual Anthropic
billing. Every API call now captures exact token counts.

  -------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Field**       **Table**      **Description**
  --------------- -------------- ------------------------------------------
  input_tokens    content_logs   Actual input tokens from API
                                 response.usage.input_tokens

  output_tokens   content_logs   Actual output tokens from API
                                 response.usage.output_tokens

  e2_cost         content_logs   Content generation cost: (input_tokens/1M
                                 \* 3) + (output_tokens/1M \* 15)

  qa_cost         content_logs   QA gates cost: sum of 3 Haiku calls

  total_cost      content_logs   e2_cost + qa_cost

  api_costs       api_costs      Granular per-call breakdown (call_type,
                  table          model, tokens, cost)
